        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-12 col-lg-9">
                <div class="image-wrapper"><div class="image_style" style="width:96%;"><picture><source sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" srcset="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/1*z59DDguTT_SZ12I26zuurg.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*z59DDguTT_SZ12I26zuurg.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/1*z59DDguTT_SZ12I26zuurg.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/1*z59DDguTT_SZ12I26zuurg.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/1*z59DDguTT_SZ12I26zuurg.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/1*z59DDguTT_SZ12I26zuurg.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/format:webp/1*z59DDguTT_SZ12I26zuurg.png 1400w" type="image/webp"/><source data-testid="og" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" srcset="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/1*z59DDguTT_SZ12I26zuurg.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/1*z59DDguTT_SZ12I26zuurg.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/1*z59DDguTT_SZ12I26zuurg.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/1*z59DDguTT_SZ12I26zuurg.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/1*z59DDguTT_SZ12I26zuurg.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/1*z59DDguTT_SZ12I26zuurg.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/1*z59DDguTT_SZ12I26zuurg.png 1400w"/><img alt="" loading="lazy" role="presentation" src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:700/1*z59DDguTT_SZ12I26zuurg.png"></picture></div><p class="mbr-description mbr-fonts-style mt-2 align-center display-12 text-muted" style="font-size:12px;">This is the system we need — a knob that turns another knob.</p><br></div></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;"><strong>Bad code thinks only of the problem at hand</strong>, and proposes the easiest solution — a knob and a knob-turner, connected by a semi-flexible rod. Bad code wins the Occam’s razor prize, at this early stage. <strong>Good code seems to be an overkill at first</strong>, and makes use of a rubber belt and 2 wheels.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-12 col-lg-9">
                <div class="image-wrapper"><div class="image_style" style="width:96%;"><picture><source sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" srcset="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/1*HNFa6ZnRJaiT0tgaeYPXMg.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*HNFa6ZnRJaiT0tgaeYPXMg.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/1*HNFa6ZnRJaiT0tgaeYPXMg.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/1*HNFa6ZnRJaiT0tgaeYPXMg.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/1*HNFa6ZnRJaiT0tgaeYPXMg.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/1*HNFa6ZnRJaiT0tgaeYPXMg.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/format:webp/1*HNFa6ZnRJaiT0tgaeYPXMg.png 1400w" type="image/webp"/><source data-testid="og" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" srcset="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/1*HNFa6ZnRJaiT0tgaeYPXMg.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/1*HNFa6ZnRJaiT0tgaeYPXMg.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/1*HNFa6ZnRJaiT0tgaeYPXMg.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/1*HNFa6ZnRJaiT0tgaeYPXMg.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/1*HNFa6ZnRJaiT0tgaeYPXMg.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/1*HNFa6ZnRJaiT0tgaeYPXMg.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/1*HNFa6ZnRJaiT0tgaeYPXMg.png 1400w"/><img alt="" loading="lazy" role="presentation" src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:700/1*HNFa6ZnRJaiT0tgaeYPXMg.png"></picture></div><p class="mbr-description mbr-fonts-style mt-2 align-center display-12 text-muted" style="font-size:12px;">One point for Bad Code! Simple, with few moving parts!</p><br></div></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><h4 class="mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4 display-5">Requirement Change! The knob will be re-located!</h4></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">As always happens in the development cycle, at some point, the customer requirement changes. In our analogy here, the customer now wants a knob turner that can rotate another knob located forward <em>and to the side of </em>the original knob, as shown below:</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-12 col-lg-9">
                <div class="image-wrapper"><div class="image_style" style="width:96%;"><picture><source sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" srcset="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/1*VfQkaesbzNsG67HnjH162Q.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*VfQkaesbzNsG67HnjH162Q.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/1*VfQkaesbzNsG67HnjH162Q.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/1*VfQkaesbzNsG67HnjH162Q.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/1*VfQkaesbzNsG67HnjH162Q.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/1*VfQkaesbzNsG67HnjH162Q.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/format:webp/1*VfQkaesbzNsG67HnjH162Q.png 1400w" type="image/webp"/><source data-testid="og" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" srcset="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/1*VfQkaesbzNsG67HnjH162Q.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/1*VfQkaesbzNsG67HnjH162Q.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/1*VfQkaesbzNsG67HnjH162Q.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/1*VfQkaesbzNsG67HnjH162Q.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/1*VfQkaesbzNsG67HnjH162Q.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/1*VfQkaesbzNsG67HnjH162Q.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/1*VfQkaesbzNsG67HnjH162Q.png 1400w"/><img alt="" loading="lazy" role="presentation" src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:700/1*VfQkaesbzNsG67HnjH162Q.png"></picture></div><p class="mbr-description mbr-fonts-style mt-2 align-center display-12 text-muted" style="font-size:12px;">Oops! Product requirement change!</p><br></div></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;"><strong>Bad code needs to add a few jerry-rigged components</strong>, making the whole system more rickety and susceptible to failure. <strong>Good code needs only slight adjustment when new requirements come in</strong>, and simply uses a longer rubber belt to solve this problem.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-12 col-lg-9">
